\section{Warning}{
Even when \code{vinterp='cubic'} the function xyY  \rarrow HVC is not \eqn{C^1}
on the plane V=1.
This is because of a change in Value spacing:
when V\eqn{\ge}1 the Value spacing is 1, but when V\eqn{\le}1 the Value spacing is 0.2.
}

